128
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,960
Maaari mo bang manatili at tulungan ako?

129
00:07:25,550 --> 00:07:27,690
Mr. Ji, baka dapat kang manatili
at tulungan si Ms. Jiang.

130
00:07:27,690 --> 00:07:29,620
Kaya kong maghanap ng bisita mag-isa.

131
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:30,690
Sigurado ka ba...

132
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:32,170
