146
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,870
Ang susunod ay isang talakayan.

147
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,840
Salubungin natin si Ms. Dianjiangchun

148
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:35,080
na may palakpakan!

149
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:36,820
-Hurray!
-Hurray!

150
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,250
Dianjiangchun!

151
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,539
Dianjiangchun!

152
00:08:43,539 --> 00:08:44,400
[Lagi sa kalsada
nire-record ang mga lasa ng mortal na mundo]

153
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,960
Hello, sa lahat.

154
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,750
Usap ngayon

155
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:50,650
dapat ay gaganapin
sa pagitan ko

156
00:08:50,690 --> 00:08:52,530
at ang aking tagapagturo, si G. Ma Wenhui.

157
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:54,870
Ngunit sa kasamaang palad,
dahil sa hindi inaasahang pangyayari,

158
00:08:54,870 --> 00:08:57,200
Si Mr. Ma ay hindi nakarating dito ngayon.

159
00:08:58,020 --> 00:08:59,100
Gayunpaman,

160
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:01,120
Ikinararangal kong mag-imbita

161
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:03,030
